Isang sikreto para kanino?

00:47:46.905 --> 00:47:49.074
Ms. Yoon. Nanay ni Sang-yeon.

00:47:50.200 --> 00:47:53.370
Sinabi mo ba sa kanya na nandito tayo?

00:47:56.039 --> 00:48:00.502
